==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Savingly
<hw>Sav"ing*ly</hw>, <pos>adv.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>In a saving
manner; with frugality or parsimony.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>So as to be finally saved from eternal
death.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q><qex>Savingly</qex> born of water and the Spirit.</q>
<rj><qau>Waterland.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Savingness</ent>⟦br⟧
